rComments: Prof Leach is absolutely amazing. He deeply cares about his students, he wants everyone to succeed, and he understands you as a person. He is not after blood and respects everyone the way they deserve. The assignments are to the point. He also has a great sense of humour. You will not regret taking his class.

Prof Leach is an absolute gem; he is very chill and caring. He is an easy grader; his lecture is brief yet comprehensible. The course includes 4 case studies that you require to respond to that never taken more than 10 minutes, a group project, and a 2000 words final assignment.
